video.title: Barbie Dreamhouse Adventures
video.synopsis: Get to know Barbie and her BFFs -- including next-door neighbor Ken -- in this animated vlog of adventures filmed inside her family's new dreamhouse.

episodes.synopsis: Barbie's friends want to be internet celebrities, but learn that fame isn't all it's cracked up to be when their goofy vlog post goes viral.
episodes.title: Virtually Famous

episodes.synopsis: When dogs are banned from the beach, Barbie and Nikki take their fight to City Hall -- and have to deal with Poppy Reardon.
episodes.title: All Dogs Go to the Beach

episodes.synopsis: Barbie and Daisy go to Barbie's hometown in Wisconsin, where they try to save her beloved Aunt Adele’s inn.
episodes.title: The Ballad of Windy Willows

episodes.synopsis: To break up the fight between Stacie and Skipper, Barbie offers to trade rooms. But soon, the Roberts sisters learn that no roommate is perfect.
episodes.title: Room Swap

episodes.synopsis: Ken and Barbie try to embark on a relaxing weekend at the spa, but end up getting caught up in an adventure with the owner's grandson.
episodes.title: Getaway and Got Away

episodes.synopsis: Trey gets hurt on the Roberts' property, so the family is extra nice to him. But Barbie suspects that the demanding neighbor is up to something.
episodes.title: Totally Spying

episodes.synopsis: Barbie and her friends try to impress a fashion idol at a mermaid convention, but things take a turn when the sisters become suspects in a mystery.
episodes.title: Barbie Roberts: Undercover Mermaid Part 1

episodes.synopsis: With her sisters in trouble for a prank gone wrong, it’s up to Barbie to prove their innocence and catch the thief.
episodes.title: Barbie Roberts: Undercover Mermaid Part 2

episodes.synopsis: The Roberts family could be evicted from their Dreamhouse unless Barbie can figure out who is behind Malibu’s sudden flea infestation.
episodes.title: A Dog's Day in Court

episodes.synopsis: Barbie feels like she's getting too old for her father-daughter tradition, so she passes it down to Chelsea. But is she really ready to let it go?
episodes.title: Balancing Act

episodes.synopsis: Thinking about the future prompts Barbie to have a dream where anything's possible -- and everything's really, really weird.
episodes.title: Life Can Be a Dream

episodes.synopsis: When Barbie discovers Duchess the horse is going to be sold, she and Stacie come up with a plan to keep her around.
episodes.title: Trey Is for Horses

episodes.synopsis: Instead of reading a book at bedtime, Chelsea tells her family a story about their puppies' secret -- and surprisingly dangerous -- lives.
episodes.title: A Dreamhouse Puppy Tale

episodes.synopsis: While trying out a new escape room with their friends, Barbie and Ken get separated from the group and wind up on an adventure of their own.
episodes.title: Time Will Tell

episodes.synopsis: Chelsea's campaign to raise money for puppy literacy continues with a miniature golf challenge that involves the whole neighborhood.
episodes.title: Putts for Pups

episodes.synopsis: From dancing to baking, the unstoppable Barbie Roberts can do anything ... except ask for help when she needs it most.
episodes.title: Pied Pupper

episodes.synopsis: Fate turns the tide on Trey and Barbie when they compete for the best spot on the beach. Back at the Dreamhouse, Stacie tries to set a world record.
episodes.title: A Day at the Beach

episodes.synopsis: Renee's desperate to impress her relatives in China, but Barbie doesn't have the heart to tell her that her "talents" need an awful lot of work.
episodes.title: A Delicate Situation

episodes.synopsis: Barbie's "Best Day Ever" starts out great ... until strange things start happening inside her family's dreamhouse. Could their new digs be cursed?
episodes.title: Welcome to the Dreamhouse!

episodes.synopsis: Barbie and her friends plan a birthday surprise for Chelsea by making over her backyard clubhouse. But their mission takes a smelly detour.
episodes.title: Clubhouse (Remix)

episodes.synopsis: Barbie puts her skills to the test when she competes on an extreme baking show against a reigning champ who loves to win -- and hates to lose.
episodes.title: Nobody's Cupcake

episodes.synopsis: The Roberts clan gets back to basics when Dad challenges them to a weekend of pioneer living. And the catch? It's all happening in their own backyard.
episodes.title: The Great Pioneer Adventure

episodes.synopsis: When Skipper snags her first babysitting job, an overprotective Barbie goes overboard trying to make sure everything runs smoothly.
episodes.title: Baby Sister Babysitter

episodes.synopsis: Barbie and her friends take a road trip to hear Daisy drop the beat at a major music festival. But Daisy keeps finding reasons to stall along the way.
episodes.title: Road Trip!

episodes.synopsis: Skipper steps in to handle her parents' 20th anniversary party when Barbie gets a once-in-a-lifetime invitation to attend Robot Con.
episodes.title: Picture Perfect Cake

episodes.synopsis: With their parents away for the night, Barbie, Skipper and Stacie recruit Ken for an elaborate plan to bring Chelsea’s imaginary “Roof Fairy” to life.
episodes.title: The Roof Fairy
